      "title": "Climate Policy Radar is back from Glasgow's COP26",
      "date": "9 December 2021",
      "thumb": "/images/climate-policy-radar-is-back-from-glasgow/image-from-ios-2-.jpg",
      "topics": ["Blog"],
      "excerpt": "We went to COP26 in Glasgow ready to share our work on our prototype, join conversations and learn from the wealth of knowledge and perspectives on offer there. Now back in the office and fired up from the experience, here\u2019s what I gained from the summit.  ",
