      "topics": ["Blog"],
      "excerpt": "The UK\u2019s two largest steel manufacturers are reportedly set receive a total of \xA3600 million to incentivise the decarbonisation of the sector. We explore how move speaks to the extent to which climate policies are interdependent on a global level.\n",
