      "topics": ["Blog"],
      "excerpt": "When we started building Climate Policy Radar, we had lots of assumptions about who our users were and what solutions would help them. In this blog post, we\u2019ll explain why we carry out user research, how we\u2019ve done it so far, what we\u2019re learning, and some of the improvements we\u2019re making in response.",
